#: 04090004.xhp#par_id3150767.29.help.text
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"SW:CHECKBOX:TP_FLD_DOKINF:CB_DOKINFFIXEDCONTENT\">Inserts the field as static content, that is, the field cannot be updated.</ahelp>"
